# **Security & IAM Engineering Showcase**  
**Isaac Esquivel de Alvear**  
🔹 **Engineering Manager | Security Engineer | IAM Specialist | Database Engineer**  
🔹 **C++, C#, Java, JavaScript | Cloud & Database Security | Automation & IAM**  

## **Overview**  
This repository showcases my expertise in **Identity & Access Management (IAM), Security Engineering, Automation, and Software Development**. It contains sample scripts, automation workflows, and security-focused tools that demonstrate my ability to enhance security infrastructures.  

## **🔐 Identity & Access Management (IAM) Automation**  
- **[PowerShell IAM Scripts](scripts/IAM_Automation.ps1)**: Automates user provisioning, role assignments, and security group management.  
- **[Okta & SailPoint API Integration](scripts/Okta_SailPoint_API.py)**: Uses Python to automate identity lifecycle management with Okta and SailPoint.  
- **[CyberArk Vault Management](scripts/CyberArk_Automation.ps1)**: Securely rotates credentials and manages privileged access.  

## **🛡️ Security Engineering & Cloud Security**  
- **[C# Security Token Validator](security/SecurityTokenValidator.cs)**: A C# implementation for validating security tokens and JWT authentication.  
- **[Java Secure File Encryption](security/SecureFileEncryption.java)**: Uses AES encryption to protect sensitive data.  
- **[AWS IAM Policy Generator](cloud/AWS_IAM_Policy_Generator.py)**: Automates AWS IAM policy creation based on security best practices.  

## **⚡ Automation & Scripting**  
- **[PowerShell System Monitoring](automation/System_Monitoring.ps1)**: Monitors system logs, detects anomalies, and alerts security teams.  
- **[SQL Security Audit Queries](database/SQL_Security_Audit.sql)**: Queries to identify security misconfigurations in SQL databases.  
- **[C++ Log Analysis Tool](automation/LogAnalysisTool.cpp)**: Parses and analyzes security logs for potential threats.  

